---
import LessonLayout from '../../layouts/LessonLayout.astro';
---
<LessonLayout
  title="Show & Tell"
  track="little-explorers"
  week={10}
  phase="Phase 4: Mini Projects"
  duration="30 min"
  emoji="🌟"
  objective="Show a friend or family member what Reachy can do"
>
  <section class="lesson-section mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-explorer-700 mb-3">🎯 Learning Objective</h2>
    <p class="bg-explorer-50 border-l-4 border-explorer-400 p-4 rounded-r-xl text-gray-700">
      Your child will prepare and deliver a short "robot show" for an audience — building communication skills and consolidating 9 weeks of learning.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="lesson-section mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">📋 Activity Steps</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-explorer-500 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">1</span>
        <div><h3 class="font-bold">Plan the Show (10 min)</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Decide: who is the audience? (grandparent, sibling, friend, stuffed animals count!) What 3 things will Reachy demonstrate? Write the "show script."</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-explorer-500 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">2</span>
        <div><h3 class="font-bold">Rehearse (10 min)</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Do a practice run. Is everything working? Make any fixes needed.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-explorer-500 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">3</span>
        <div><h3 class="font-bold">Show Time! (10 min)</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Perform for the audience. Take a bow at the end!</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lesson-section mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">💻 Code Snippet</h2>
    <pre is:raw class="bg-gray-900 text-green-300 rounded-xl p-5 overflow-x-auto text-sm leading-relaxed"><code># show_and_tell.py — Week 10: Little Explorers
import time

class ReachyMock:
    def say(self, msg): print(f"🤖 {msg}"); time.sleep(1)
    def wave(self): print("👋 *waves*"); time.sleep(1)
    def show_emotion(self, e): print(f"😊 *shows {e} face*"); time.sleep(1)
    def dance_move(self, m): print(f"💃 *{m}*"); time.sleep(1)
    def bow(self): print("🙇 *takes a bow*"); time.sleep(1)

try:
    from reachy_mini import ReachyMini
    robot = ReachyMini()
except Exception:
    robot = ReachyMock()

# THE SHOW — customise this!
robot.say("Hello everyone! I am Reachy Mini!")
robot.wave()
robot.say("Watch what I can do!")
robot.show_emotion("excited")
robot.dance_move("the robot wave")
robot.say("I learned all this with my friend!")
robot.bow()
robot.say("Thank you for watching!")</code></pre>
  </section>

  <section class="lesson-section mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">💬 Reflection Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-xl p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-yellow-800">🌟 "What was the audience's favourite part?"</p></div>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-xl p-4"><p class="font-semibold text-yellow-800">🌟 "What would you add to the show next time?"</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lesson-section mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">👪 Parent Tips</h2>
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-gray-700">
      <p>💡 This lesson is as much about public speaking confidence as robotics. Even a teddy bear audience works!</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</LessonLayout>
